messages.text: I maybe, kinda, sorta…might be stuck inside one of the lockers at school.
I’m sorry, I fell off my bed laughing.
Come on, I’m serious, I’m freaking out in here
What the hell are you doing at school at 1am?!
I wanted to play that prank on Dana
While I was trying to write “BITCH”on her locker, the janitor came, so I locked myself in mine
You didn’t think to go to the bathroom?
Shut up and get me out of here
You know this place is creepy at night
I was walking down the hall, and heard these footsteps behind me
Srsly. A teacher murdered one of his students there in the 70s
This guy Mr. Sampson asked one of the students to stay after school
CAN WE PLEASE TALK ABOUT ANYTHING ELSE
Just come get me out of here
Well, whoever it is, luckily you’re safe inside a locker lol
They stopped in front of my locker
Ask them to get you out!
Maybe they are scared and know someone is in there, and that’s freaking them out?
Can you see anything through the grate
Do you think I should call the cops?
No, I think you should say something
Fine, I’ll call the cops, but you’re probably going to get in trouble
Ten minutes. I had to sneak out obvi
I knew I shouldn’t have come here. My heart is pounding
They’ll probably just go away. Stay still
OMG, they just started pushing something in through the grate
I don’t know, it’s too dark
I just asked him to let me out, and he started laughing!
Do you think this is someone trying to get revenge?
I mean, you’ve pissed off a lot of people with things you’ve done
I screamed to leave me alone, and they started laughing again
It sounds like they are tearing something
Omg!! The person is starting to duct tape the cracks!!
They said they are on their way. Just try to be calm
He’s duct taping the grate!! I’ll be stuck in here with the cockroaches!!
That’s not why he’s duct taping the grate
My little sister Amy finally owned up to who gave her the black eye she had last week
Said that you took her to the woods and smacked her around
I told you never to lay a hand on my sister
All you do is bully people, now it’s your turn
What is that hose you’re putting against the grate!?
Not me. It’s a fireman friend of mine from the other district
And yeah, he’s got the hookup ; )
Oh come on, Jenn, you know my fear of drowning
PLEASE STOP JENN! I’LL DO ANYTHING
I told you. Keep your filthy hands off my little sister
GET ME OUT OF HERE!!!!!  PLEASE!!!
See you in the morning. If ya make it : )
